To enhance metadata and reporting capabilities, we will be implementing a new data visualization tool, Tableau, to provide more interactive and dynamic insights. This will enable users to easily explore and analyze data, identify trends, and make data-driven decisions. Additionally, we will be creating a new dashboard to provide a centralized location for key performance indicators (KPIs) and metrics, allowing for easier tracking and monitoring of business performance.
